'''Elon University''' is a selective private [[liberal arts university]] in [[Elon, North Carolina]], [[United States]].<ref>The university is classified as selective by the CIS Higher Education Directory 2010, Council of International Schools, p. 204</ref> Formerly known as Elon College, it became Elon University on June 1, 2001. The {{convert|600|acre|1|adj=on}} campus is a [[botanical garden]] and features oak trees, brick sidewalks, fountains, and lakes. Elon is ranked by the [[U.S.News & World Report]] as the second best Regional University in the [[Southern United States|South]].

